descCRN['10090&TermDescription=Fall%202017'] = '<p>Notes:<br />*First Year Course only; first day attendance required*<br/>An introduction to the principles of genetics, including topics from classical Mendalian concepts to the contemporary molecular biology of the gene. Three lecture hours per week.</p>';
